Angular 15:		November 16, 2022
				Standalone components is stable 
				Modules are getting replaced
					provideHttpClient instead of HttpClientModule
					provideRouter instead of RouterModule forRoot/ forChild
				Directive Composition API
					using already defined directives in other directives/components
				Image Directive (NgOptimized Image) is stable use ngSrc instead of src
				Guards can be used within the routes canActive using lamda'src
				Better Stack traces
				